            <p>Devometric uses RAG to ensure our assessments and recommendations reflect the latest AI tools, techniques, and best practices in software development. This means when we mention a tool like "Claude Code" or "Cursor," we're drawing from current, accurate information rather than potentially outdated training data.</p>
